      "date": "2024-08-13 15:19:17.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2:\n> \n> Tim, it's this series Andreas was thinking of.  LU-16565 gives the rationale the removal, though it's hopefully mostly obvious.\n> \n> Perhaps you want to convert these to coccinelle patches?  I did it by hand, heh.\n\nThis seems easy enough to write a coccinelle script for. The other patch series I had only took ~10-15 minutes once I had the script ready. I think I finally have a good process for semi-automating these cleanup patch series. I'll push my scripts to `contrib` (along with a small README perhaps).\n\nI think the only limiting factor now is whether people want to review all these patches. :)",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
